These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, analyst
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, gospel
1. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | analyst | architect |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | trance  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: frog, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | hamster   | frog      |
| Transport   | helicopter | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, disco
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski
1. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | metal    |
| Transport     | trike | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, romance
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, metal
1. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | romance |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | metal |

 #################################

 
